  "description": "Single voice — an 808-derived sub kick pitched down 36 semitones below standard. Below rhythm. Below bass. A geological event with a 4-second decay. The body IS the space. Every other voice silent. XVC routes the sub pulse back into its own character parameter creating a self-modulating topology. One thing, going very deep.",
